{"title":"mysql 下 计算 两点 经纬度 之间的距离","date":"2018-06-21T22:58:00.000Z","link":"post/125","categories":["DataBase"],"updated":"2019-04-27T13:23:24.999Z","content":"<p>公式如下，<strong>单位米：</strong><br>第一点经纬度：lng1 lat1<br>第二点经纬度：lng2 lat2**<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">round(6378.138*2*asin(sqrt(pow(sin( (lat1*pi()/180-lat2*pi()/180)/2),2)+cos(lat1*pi()/180)*cos(lat2*pi()/180)* pow(sin( (lng1*pi()/180-lng2*pi()/180)/2),2)))*1000)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p><strong>例如：</strong><br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">SELECT store_id,lng,lat, ROUND(6378.138*2*ASIN(SQRT(POW(SIN((22.299439*PI()/180-lat*PI()/180)/2),2)+COS(22.299439*PI()/180)*COS(lat*PI()/180)*POW(SIN((114.173881*PI()/180-lng*PI()/180)/2),2)))*1000) AS juli</span><br><span class=\"line\">FROM store_info</span><br><span class=\"line\">ORDER BY juli DESC</span><br><span class=\"line\">LIMIT 316</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>参考资料如下：<br><a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_8da982ac0101jeh5.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_8da982ac0101jeh5.html</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"git提示服务器与本地有冲突","link":"post/126"},"next":{"title":"微信小程序js端生命周期问题","link":"post/124"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/125/"}